>\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">severity</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Message.html#Lean.MessageSeverity\">MessageSeverity</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">removedVersion?</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/ErrorExplanation.html#Lean.ErrorExplanation.Metadata\">Metadata</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/ErrorExplanation.lean#L18-L31","name":"Lean.ErrorExplanation.Metadata","line":18,"kind":"structure","docLink":"./Lean/ErrorExplanation.html#Lean.ErrorExplanation.Metadata","doc":"Metadata for an error explanation.\n\n* `summary` gives a short description of the error\n* `sinceVersion` indicates the version of Lean in which an error with this error name was introduced\n* `severity` is the severity of the diagnostic\n* `removedVersion` indicates the version of Lean in which this error name was retired, if applicable\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">structure</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/ErrorExplanation.html#Lean.ErrorExplanation.Metadata\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">ErrorExplanation</span>.<span class=\"name\">Metadata</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>"}]}